<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFBCFF9D64BAFE03FBB9FDB0" pageId="12" pageNumber="229" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFBCFF9D64BAFE03FBB9FDB0" blockId="12.[151,1128,476,563]" pageId="12" pageNumber="229">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBCFF9D64BAFE03FE42FE50" bold="true" box="[151,403,476,499]" pageId="12" pageNumber="229">Differential diagnosis.</emphasis>
This species is very similar to 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFBCFF9D66C8FE03FCA9FE50" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[741,888,476,499]" genus="Pseudochillus" pageId="12" pageNumber="229" rank="species" species="helferi" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Kaszabochillus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBCFF9D66C8FE03FD2DFE50" box="[741,764,476,499]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="229">P.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBCFF9D6724FE03FCF3FE50" box="[777,802,476,499]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="229">K.</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFBCFF9D671FFE03FCA9FE50" box="[818,888,476,499]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="229">helferi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="AA9D5784FFBCFF9D67ADFE03FC05FE50" box="[896,980,476,499]" pageId="12" pageNumber="229" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
but differs in absence of mid-longitudinal impression on pronotum and punctate lateral margins of pronotum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
